      • loadRessource

        public java.io.File loadRessource(java.lang.String configPath)
                           throws java.io.IOException
        This file creates a written configuration in your plugin folder. Subfolders must be splitted with "/" like folder/config.yml. Don't forget dataendings. Also check, if the path of your internal configuration is similar to the path of the pluginfolder.
        Parameters:
        configPath - the path of your configuration. Must be similar to their real location.
        Returns:
        the File itself
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - if the system cannot create the file due input-output errors
